videos.description: Dylan Osetkowski uses great anticipation on the steal and then slams it down on the other end for Texas.
videos.headline: Osetkowski gets steal and slam for Longhorns

videos.description: Davide Moretti gets a great pass to Brandone Francis who makes the long 3-pointer for Texas Tech.
videos.headline: Moretti finds Francis for a 3-pointer

videos.description: TTU's Keenan Evans uses perfect timing to make the layup and draw the foul creating a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Evans beats MoBamba on layup

videos.description: Keenan Evans goes around the defender and finishes with the lay-in for the Red Raiders.
videos.headline: Evans works his way around defender for layup

videos.description: Keenan Evans stays hot as he fakes out the defender and scores for Texas Tech.
videos.headline: Evans sinks step-back jumper

videos.description: Mohamed Bamba is bumped in to by his own teammate and is helped off the court.
videos.headline: MoBamba slow to get up after taking low hit

videos.description: Jarrett Culver cuts through the defense and makes the reverse layup for Texas Tech.
videos.headline: TTU's Culver uses nice move on layup

videos.description: Kerwin Roach II gets the steal and finds Jase Febres who finishes with the slam to give the Longhorns the lead.
videos.headline: Texas takes lead with steal and slam

videos.description: Texas keeps the momentum with a Mohamed Bamba dunk.
videos.headline: MoBamba throws down big dunk

videos.description: Keenan Evans draws contact on his way to the basket and sinks his free throw to force overtime against Texas.
videos.headline: Evans draws foul to force OT versus Texas

videos.description: Keenan Evans kicks it out to Jarrett Culver who drives to the basket and finishes with a slam for Texas Tech.
videos.headline: Culver pumps up crowd with huge slam

videos.description: Keenan Evans sinks a jumper with one second remaining in overtime to lead Texas Tech to a win over Texas.
videos.headline: Evans comes up big with game winner vs. Texas

videos.description: Keenan Evans comes through with the winning basket in overtime and drops 38 points in Texas Tech's victory against rival Texas.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Evans puts up heroic performance for No. 10 Texas Tech) 2018/01/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Evans puts up heroic performance for No. 10 Texas Tech
